      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must be under version control with documented test suite passing rate ≥ 95%.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022 R2 is used under institutional license with version control. Regression test suite reports 97% pass rate. Software quality documentation meets MRL 2 requirements."
    },
    {
