    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements given medium model influence and high decision consequence. Uncertainty quantification has been performed and confirms the nominal hemolysis prediction satisfies RH < 1 across the UQ ensemble. The overall credibility evidence is sufficient to support the regulatory submission decision for the Class II CPB device under the stated COU.",
